## **🎯 Benefits Over React Shadcn-UI**

1. **Better Performance** - No JavaScript bundle bloat
2. **Better SEO** - Server-rendered HTML
3. **Better Accessibility** - Native HTML semantics
4. **Better Rails Integration** - Works with forms, helpers, etc.
5. **Better Maintainability** - Single language (Ruby + HTML + CSS)
6. **Better Caching** - Server-side component caching

